<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The following are some frequently asked questions about installing and using ITOM Container Deployment Foundation (CDF).</p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; background: none rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 500; margin: 25px 0px 6px; overflow: hidden; padding-top: 0em; padding-bottom: 0.17em; border-bottom: none; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(0, 115, 231) !important; font-size: 24px !important;">What are the recommended deployment modes for CDF?</h2><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.3em 0px 0px 1.6em; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><li style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0.1em;">One master node, at least three worker nodes, and a separate NFS server.</li><li style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0.1em;">Multiple master nodes, at least three worker nodes, and a separate NFS server.</li></ul><font color="#212529" face="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><div><font color="#212529" face="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br></span></font></div></span></font><h2><font color="#212529" face="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol"><span style="font-size: 15px;">Can i upgrade the suite images in CDF?</span></font></h2><div><font color="#212529" face="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol"><span style="font-size: 15px;">You will need to log in the management portal,click SUITE &gt;&nbsp;</span></font><span style="background-color: transparent; letter-spacing: 0.15pt; text-transform: initial; color: rgb(64, 0, 64); font-size: x-large; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;"><a href="https://docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/index.php?title=Special:Upload&amp;wpDestFile=https://docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/f/fb/2018.04/attachments/17859066/22185968.png" title="File:https://docs.microfocus.com/mediawiki/images/f/fb/2018.04/attachments/17859066/22185968.png" style="letter-spacing: 0.15pt; background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;">22185968.png</a></span><span style="background-color: transparent; text-transform: initial; color: rgb(64, 0, 64); font-size: x-large; letter-spacing: 1.13333px; font-family: MetricHPE_Medium, serif;">&nbsp;&gt; Update to upgrade suite.</span></div><h2>Will the logs located in a pod be deleted when the pod is deleted?</h2><h2>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529;
letter-spacing:.15pt">All the suite logs are currently stored within the
persistent volume, so you will not lose them if the pods go down. This applies
to both on-premise and cloud-based deployments.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:11.5pt;font-family:
&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#212529;
letter-spacing:.15pt">How do I restart the CDF cluster (foundation components)?<o:p></o:p></span></p></h2><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Run the following commands to restart the CDF cluster:</p><pre style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 240); padding: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 1.25em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: auto;">cd ${K8S_HOME}/bin
./kube-restart.sh</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span id="Do_I_need_to_add_exceptions_to_the_firewall_policy.3F" style="box-sizing: border-box;"></span><span id="Do_I_need_to_add_exceptions_to_the_firewall_policy.3F" class="mw-headline" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Do I need to add exceptions to the firewall policy?</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Browsers access CDF via HTTPS ports (TCP/5443). End users need to add it to the firewall exception policy.</p>